name: Red light district
description:
As I was staring at the ceiling light in my room, I took a photo of it and I busted out of the house. Later that night, I decided to make a double exposure photo adding this street light to the photo.

Gear I used
Camera: Nikon FM10 
Lens: 35~70 1:3.5~4.8 
Film: Fujicolor C200

Technique: Double Exposure
